# Same-file call inside Astro frontmatter: `run` calls `helper`, both defined in the frontmatter
# block. Proves the embedded-SFC pattern's offset remap: extract_ecmascript resolves the call
# against the frontmatter's own byte range, then shift_offsets remaps both def and ref lines back
# into the full .astro document before the resolver ever sees them.
Component.astro:6 Call Component.astro:2
